{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c7d5eb42df","title":"对李达来信的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6ffad0dced","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":10,"articleId":"c7d5eb42df"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji48","name":"毛泽东全集第48卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/48-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji48":{"comments":[{"id":"9f746a8246","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"c7d5eb42df","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李达，原任全国人大常委会委员、武汉大学校长。当时被错误地打成所谓武汉大学“三家村黑头目”，戴上“叛徒”“地主分子”的帽子，并被开除党籍。1966年7月19日，他给毛泽东写信，请求解救他。毛泽东见信后即写了这个批语。8月10日，中共中央书记处常务书记陶铸接到毛泽东的批语后，立即批示：“即送任重同志。任重，即王任重，当时任中共湖北省委第一书记。8月24日，李达受迫害致死。1980年，中共中央书记处批准湖北省委的决定，为李达平反昭雪，恢复名誉，恢复党籍。"}],"contents":[{"id":"11e8b8875e","type":"title","text":"对李达来信的批语”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"c7d5eb42df"},{"id":"9f746a8246","type":"paragraph","text":"海铸同志阅后，转任重同志的处","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"c7d5eb42df"},{"id":"85183a9af6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"c7d5eb42df"},{"id":"e0ccebe8e2","type":"paragraph","text":"八月十日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"c7d5eb42df"}],"page":{"id":"bad7d863dc","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"c7d5eb42df","start":467,"end":467}}}},"__N_SSG":true}